<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٧١٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4035">ابْنِ جُرَيْجٍ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4385">عَطَاءٌ </a>: سَمِعَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">جَابِرَ بْنَ عَبْدِ اللهِ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«كُنَّا لَا نَأْكُلُ مِنْ لُحُومِ بُدْنِنَا فَوْقَ ثَلَاثِ مِنًى،<span class="c5"> فَرَخَّصَ لَنَا النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فَقَالَ:</span> كُلُوا وَتَزَوَّدُوا، فَأَكَلْنَا وَتَزَوَّدْنَا،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٧٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ لِعَطَاءٍ:</span> أَقَالَ: حَتَّى جِئْنَا الْمَدِينَةَ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> لَا».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>